ISLAMABAD, Oct 09 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb said on Sunday that Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif would attend Seerat Conference in Lahore today.
In a tweet she said that he would also deliver a speech in the conference which would be telecast live by Pakistan Television.
